///notes to successfully run kafka on system

type the below commands in kafka/bin/config folder CMD

zookeeper-server-start.bat C:\kafka\config\zookeeper.properties -----------------check for port 2181

kafka-server-start.bat C:\kafka\config\server.properties--------------------------check for port 9092

Command to create topic:
kafka-topics.bat --create --topic javaguides --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

Command to read events:
kafka-console-consumer.bat --topic javaguides --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

